th captivating event cards. Make strategic choices on each card to face the corresponding outcomes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473240/extras/1872d78885038897c550301f15c9001a.poster.avif?t=1693200316\" width=498 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473240/extras/1872d78885038897c550301f15c9001a.webm?t=1693200316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473240/extras/1872d78885038897c550301f15c9001a.mp4?t=1693200316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Battle System</strong>: Engage in combat using regular dice for basic attacks, or combine regular and elemental dice to unleash powerful skills and gain corresponding effects.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473240/extras/dad3be9b439ff805d25a94f4c4280af7.poster.avif?t=1693200316\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473240/extras/dad3be9b439ff805d25a94f4c4280af7.webm?t=1693200316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473240/extras/dad3be9b439ff805d25a94f4c4280af7.mp4?t=1693200316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Boss System</strong>: Confront formidable boss monsters on each dungeon floor. Defeating them unlocks deeper levels of the dungeon to conquer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473240/extras/25f45d38f6ff3d1a1fae0d586b540970.poster.avif?t=1693200316\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstati